iors: 51|Cage Warriors: 51]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2012|December|31}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 3:40\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n| |{{small|Won the [[Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors Lightweight Championship|Cage Warriors Lightweight Championship]].}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 11\u20132\n| Dave Hill\n| Submission (rear-naked choke)\n| [[2012 in Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors: 47|Cage Warriors: 47]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2012|June|2}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4:10\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n| {{small|Won the [[Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors Featherweight Championship|Cage Warriors Featherweight Championship]].}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 10\u20132\n| Steve O'Keefe\n| KO (elbows)\n| [[2012 in Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors: 45|Cage Warriors: 45]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2012|February|18}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1:35\n| [[Kentish Town]], England\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 9\u20132\n| Aaron Jahnsen\n| TKO (punches)\n| [[2011 in Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors: Fight Night 2|Cage Warriors: Fight Night 2]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2011|September|8}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 3:29\n| [[Amman]], Jordan\n|{{small|Lightweight bout.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 8\u20132\n| Artur Sowinski\n| TKO (punches)\n| Celtic Gladiator 2: Clash of the Giants\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2011|June|11}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1:12\n| [[Portlaoise]], Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7\u20132\n| Paddy Doherty\n| KO (punch)\n| Immortal Fighting Championship 4\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2011|April|16}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 0:04\n| [[Letterkenny]], Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 6\u20132\n| Mike Wood\n| KO (punches)\n| Cage Contender 8\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2011|March|12}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 0:16\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5\u20132\n| Hugh Brady\n| TKO (punches)\n| Chaos FC 8\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2011|February|12}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2:31\n| [[Derry]], Northern Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4\u20132\n| [[Joseph Duffy (fighter)|Joseph Duffy]]\n| Submission (arm-triangle choke)\n| [[2010 in Cage Warriors#Cage Warriors 39: The Uprising|Cage Warriors 39: The Uprising]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2010|November|27}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 0:38\n| [[Cork (city)|Cork]], Ireland\n|{{small|Lightweight bout.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4\u20131\n| Connor Dillon\n| TKO (corner stoppage)\n| Chaos FC 7\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2010|October|9}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4:22\n| [[Derry]], Northern Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 3\u20131\n| Stephen Bailey\n| TKO (punches)\n| K.O.: The Fight Before Christmas\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2008|December|12}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1:22\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n|\n|-\n|{{no2}}Loss\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\u20131\n|Artemij Sitenkov\n| Submission (kneebar)\n| Cage of Truth 3\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2008|June|28}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1:09<!--<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cUNSkuZKMXk|title=UFC Fighter Conor McGregor vs Safin Sofian v \u2013 1ST MMA LOSS \u2013 FULL FIGHT|work=YouTube|accessdate=23 October 2014}}</ref>-->\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n|{{small|Featherweight debut.}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\u20130\n| Mo Taylor\n| TKO (punches)\n| [[2008 in Cage Rage Championships#Cage Rage Contenders - Ireland vs. Belgium|Cage Rage Contenders - Ireland vs. Belgium]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2008|May|3}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1:06\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n|\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1\u20130\n| Gary Morris\n| TKO (punches)\n| Cage of Truth 2\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2008|March|8}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 0:08\n| [[Dublin]], Ireland\n|\n|}\n<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sherdog.com/fighter/Conor-McGregor-29688|title=Conor \"Notorious\" McGregor|website=Sherdog|accessdate=8 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Professional boxing record==\n{{BoxingRecordSummary\n|draws=\n|nc=\n|ko-wins=\n|ko-losses=1\n|dec-wins=\n|dec-losses=\n|dq-wins=\n|dq-losses=\n}}\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:95%\"\n|-\n!{{abbr|No.|Number}}\n!Result\n!Record\n!Opponent\n!Type\n!Round, time\n!Date\n!Age\n!Location\n!Notes\n|-\n|1\n|{{no2}}Loss\n|0\u20131\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Floyd Mayweather Jr.]]\n|{{abbr|TKO|Technical knockout}}\n|10 (12), {{small|1:05}}\n|[[Floyd Mayweather Jr. vs. Conor McGregor|26 August 2017]]\n|{{Age in years and days|1988|7|14|2017|8|26}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[T-Mobile Arena]], [[Paradise, Nevada]], US}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Biography|Ireland}}\n* [[List of current UFC fighters]]\n* [[List of Irish UFC fighters]]\n* [[List of male mixed martial artists]]\n* [[Ultimate Fighting Championship rankings]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sisterlinks|d=Q5162259|c=category:Conor McGregor|n=no|b=no|v=no|voy=no|s=no|wikt=no|m=no|mw=no|species=no}}\n* {{BoxRec|802658}}\n* {{UFC|conor-mcgregor}}\n* {{Sherdog|29688}}\n* [http://www.sbgireland.com/ SBG Ireland]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ach}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=1st [[List of UFC champions#Featherweight Championship|UFC Interim Featherweight Champion]] |years=11 July&n