odhomepage.com/new-mormon-stake-center-opens-on-sunset-road/|title=New Mormon Stake Center opens on Sunset Road|date=26 August 2015|publisher=FW Publishing|work=Brentwood Home Page}}</ref>\n|\n|  \n|\n| 2015 \n| [[Manhattan, New York]] \n| {{Flag|United States}} \n| [[Catholic Church|Catholic]] \n|\n|-\n| Beomeo Cathedral\n|2,463{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|\n|  \n|\n| 2013\u20132016 \n| [[Daegu]]\n|{{Flag|Republic of Korea}}\n| [[Catholic Church|Catholic]] ([[Latin Church|Latin]]) \n| \n|-\n|[[Cathedral Basilica of St. Francis of Assisi (Santa Fe)]]\n| 2,322{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|\n|  \n|\n| 1869\u20131887\n| [[Santa Fe, New Mexico]] \n|{{Flag|United States}} \n| [[Catholic Church|Catholic]] \n|\n|-\n|[[Our Lady of Dolours Syro-Malabar Catholic Basilica]]\n|2,300{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|\n|  \n|\n| 1929\u20132005 \n| [[Thrissur]]\n|{{Flag|India}}\n| [[Catholic Church|Catholic]] ([[Syro-Malabar Catholic Church|Syro-Malabar]]) \n| It has the third tallest tower in Asia{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|-\n|[[St. John's Cathedral (Seongnam)]]\n|2,260{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|\n|  \n|\n| 1994\u20132002 \n| [[Seongnam]]\n|{{Flag|Republic of Korea}}\n| [[Catholic Church|Catholic]] ([[Latin Church|Latin]]) \n| Until 2009, largest church in East Asia{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|-\n|[[Basilica of St. John the Baptist]]\n| 2,135{{Citation needed|date=February 2019}}\n|\n| 64,040<ref name=\"Geology of the Catholic Basilica of St. John the Baptist, St. John's, Newfoundland\">{{cite journal |url=http://www.gac.ca/wp/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/v31no1partial.pdf | title=Geology of the Catholic Basilica of St. John the Baptist, St. John's, Newfoundland |work=Geoscience Canada|  volume=31 |number=1 |pages=1\u201310 |publisher=Geological Association of Canada |date=March 2004 |accessdate=29 May 2015}}</ref>\n|\n| 1839\u201355\n| [[St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador|St. John's]] \n|{{Flag|Canada}}\n| [[