9/http://hitotoki.org/classic/sofia/004|archivedate=30 March 2010|work=Hitotoki}}</ref>\n|\n| 86,000<ref>[http://15veka.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ENG_PATRIARCHAL-CATHEDRAL-STAUROPIGIAL.pdf ''15 Century Bulgaria Foundation''] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180425183233/http://15veka.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/ENG_PATRIARCHAL-CATHEDRAL-STAUROPIGIAL.pdf |date=25 April 2018 }} (15 \u0432\u0435\u043a\u0430 \u0411\u042a\u041b\u0413\u0410\u0420\u0418\u042f) website, article with title ''Patriarchal cathedral stauropigial memorial church St. Alexander Nevsky'' (pdf)</ref>\n|\n| 1882\u20131912 \n| [[Sofia]] \n|{{Flag|Bulgaria}}\n| [[Eastern Orthodox Church|Eastern Orthodox]] ([[Bulgarian Orthodox Church|Bulgaria]]) \n|\n|-\n|[[Crystal Cathedral]]\n|3,030<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.archdaily.com/445618/ad-classics-the-crystal-cathedral-philip-johnson |title=AD Classics: The Crystal Cathedral / Philip Johnson |author=Jones, Rennie |date=6 November 2013 |website=Arch Daily |accessdate=22 April 2019}}</ref><!--Reference states area is 32,000 ft2 without clarifying whether this is interior or exterior area. However, the geometry is shown in this reference (essentially a four-pointed star) along with overall dimensions (400 ft long by 200 ft wide).-->\n|\n|\n|\n|1977\u20131980\n|[[Garden Grove, California]]\n|{{Flag|United States}}\n|[[Catholic Church|Catholic]] ([[Latin Church|Latin]])\n|Consecrated as the Christ Cathedral<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://christcathedralcalifornia.org/explore/about-christ-cathedral/|title=Christ Cathedral: A Galvanizing Cultural Icon and Center for Worship|publisher=Christ Catholic Cathedral}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Westminster Abbey]]\n| 2,972<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.westminster-abbey.org/media/4101/abbey-dimensions-for-web.pdf|title=Abbey Dimensions|website=Westminster Abbey}}</ref>\n|\n|  \n|\n| 960\u201318c \n| [[London]] \n|{{Flag|United Kingdom}} \n| [[Anglican Communion|Anglican]] ([[Church of England]]) \n|\n|-\n|[[M